  "text": "The ability of the RDKA84 mutant and its parental strain MVF-84 to survive inside J774A.1, a murine macrophage cell line (ATCC TIB-67), and MAC-T, an established bovine mammary epithelial cell line, was determined as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
